headline: Here’s Why Madison Large Cap Fund Sold Elevance Health (ELV) in Q3
summary: Madison Investments, an investment advisor, released its “Madison Large Cap Fund” third-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. headline: CVS Health Lifts Adjusted EPS Outlook: What's Driving It?
summary: CVS raises its full-year EPS outlook after a strong quarter, driven by gains across all segments and solid pharmacy growth.

headline: Did Elevance Health's (ELV) Reaffirmed 2025 Outlook Signal Operational Stability Amid Industry Pressures?
summary: Elevance Health recently reaffirmed its 2025 earnings guidance and projected a benefit expense ratio of about 90.0% during presentations to investors and at healthcare industry conferences in early November 2025. This ongoing transparency and emphasis on operational stability comes as the company addresses industry headwinds, including margin pressures and increased competition in government-sponsored programs.
